{"tid":98390,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣某間海南雞店","createTime":"2017-01-28T11:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T11:38:55.000Z","uid":19182,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4be83ecb5fc73749208520aec76394dc756ef509","tid":98390,"uid":19182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:18:16.000Z","msg":"我們一行五人，其中三人先到<br />\n當時我們要求五杯水，但是只來了兩杯<br />\n五分鐘後我們再問，但並沒有理會我。<br />\n再過了十分鐘，其餘兩人到了，並再次要求三杯水。可是，亦只有給我們兩杯水，所以我們再問，然後侍應的態度極差，反指很忙，但當時只有寥寥數台顧客。之後她再給了我們兩杯，這次我們沒有再容忍，並怒嗆那位侍應，然而她仍然頂嘴。在怒斥期間，又有一位侍應拿了一杯水過來，真係九唔搭八<br />\n食物方面，叫了五個飯，但有兩個飯裏有生米，換飯時的態度亦十分差<br />\n總之，當天過了一個十分離譜的晚飯，勸喻各位不要光顧。"},{"pid":"a626624b1ef272baf4e04153680dbaca8a57c905","tid":98390,"uid":34243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"我上錯左openrice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0adafa975dcab2eddb044ef263ab1e8b36a443de","tid":98390,"uid":65538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:20:11.000Z","msg":"係咪路德圍個間?"},{"pid":"1e55761a69ddc778cbe87db38f7e65efc1c708e6","tid":98390,"uid":6439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:20:42.000Z","msg":"任嗌架喎"},{"pid":"1d7e1d72090506066e07f97367eaf982d29ca701","tid":98390,"uid":49366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:21:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上錯左openrice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca04ad5d0967c6cf51c288877e295a27e7e1529","tid":98390,"uid":19182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:21:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>任嗌架喎</blockquote><br />\n但係佢冇攞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ae6e30649fd31413b49edaaef544931ce4ff27","tid":98390,"uid":19182,"like":0,"dislik